<br>
Happy hunting necros  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/upopinfearash.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Popin Fearash</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/8/01 8:42:38 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> Yeah, we got the new grp dmf spell: Dead *Men* floating lvl49 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uvermintide.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vermintide</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/8/01 11:06:29 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> Having specific spells drop off specific mobs instead of having random spell drops.<br>
<br>
What a good idea. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uqhue.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qhue</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/9/01 8:02:30 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Doubting necros</span><hr size=1> I looked over to the necro boards where they pointed to this thread with very doubting glances...<br>
<br>
Yes the new spells are in, yes the Gangrenous Touch of Zum'ull drops off Grand Advisor Zum'ull (note the name similarity).   One of our guild necros was lifetapping up a storm on fully MR mobs in North Tov last night and cackling himself silly. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uvehn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vehn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/9/01 9:06:23 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> Summon corpse anyone? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usharafeyheart.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shara Feyheart</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/9/01 11:12:01 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> Improved Summon Corpse dropped off a named mob from the 3 spawn room right by the fork in the betrayer tunnel.<br>
<br>
Sennii <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usvenalo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>svenalo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/9/01 4:12:02 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> A potentially bad idea as it raises contention for the camps when the spells are that desirable. You get all sorts of stupid political crap happening, then, which was the one thing random drops actually did stop from happening. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udejichan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Deji Chan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/9/01 4:17:04 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> WTF is an Improved Summon Corpse? :>  I'd say improved if it can summon all 30+ corpses at a single time in less than 10 secs and requires no coffins!<br>
<br>
~* Dejiko Soulblighter *~<br>
52 Garden Tool & LVL 60 Rare-Drop NEC Pet <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uspellbounder.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Spellbounder</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.sinfest.net/slick.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/9/01 5:19:02 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> the spell that requires cheaper, stackable coffins instead of huge coffins that require an entire inventory space. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uayashii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ayashii</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/9/01 11:08:47 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> Talking about Conjure Corpse? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uvermintide.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vermintide</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/10/01 12:44:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> Summon Corpse 2 has been in the game a long time.  But it's always been a random drops.<br>
<br>
I like the idea of spells being static drops because in a way, drop spells are probably the most important caster loot in the game, and alot of casters are often complaining about NBG loot groups because most equipment drops are melee oriented.<br>
<br>
This would kind of level the playing field. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uremfin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Remfin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/10/01 7:22:57 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> The name of the scroll is &quot;Improved Summon Corpse&quot;, but it scribes &quot;Conjure Corpse&quot; - hence the confusion <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uallaxuldarksoul.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Allaxul Darksoul</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/10/01 9:16:44 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> Correct, it seems the name on the scroll is not actually linked to the spell itself so it can be wrong.<br>
<br>
Another example is to this day our 49 spell &quot;Bond of Death&quot; scroll is actually labelled &quot;Lifetap AE IV&quot; from a series of spells that didn't work out way back in EQ beta.<br>
<br>
That one even got me petitioned because someone thought I was trying to scam him with a fake spell scroll. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ucryptkeeper.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Crypt Keeper</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/10/01 12:39:46 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> I was there last nite, Infusion dropped off a named mob also<br>
<br>
<br>
Mr.C <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usayleth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sayleth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/10/01 3:46:03 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> Conjure Corpse actually reads as 'New Summon Corpse' on the scroll, thus the posts when 'improved' was mentioned.<br>
<br>
Sayleth <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usouthernkreuz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Southern Kreuz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/10/01 3:51:29 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> lol summon corpse was brought up in this thread for one reason and apparently you didnt catch it...<br>
<br>
anyone remember how to get summon corpse?...<br>
<br>
ishva...splitpaw...<br>
<br>
the above poster was just mentioning that how they have done new spells on named spawns before...<br>
<br>
southern <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukeadaiansongborne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Keadaian Songborne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/11/01 10:36:28 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> I'd like to see all dropped spells taken off the mobs and made into quests instead.  Makes far more sense...  Wise old wizard long past his dragon killing days tells a young adventurous wizard that he'll teach him to harness the power of the sun to strike directly at his foes if only you'll do me this one small favor....<br>
<br>
Yes, I know there are a few spells that are quested already.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uleriche1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Leriche1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/12/01 1:37:45 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Necro spells in Chardok</span><hr size=1> Sad thing is...They add a disease Check lifetap..and lower the Resists on all NPC mobs.  Even Tormax takes a fat 720 from touch of night now.  This new spell is cool, but kinda late imo.  As far as group DMF, i've been beggin for that spell for so long...and now they put it in a dungeon where i have no clue where to go /sigh  Guess it's time to just get some AE action going and find korucust or whatever <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=3030.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadControl?topicID=3030.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3030.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3030.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboa